<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quiz</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffecb3;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .question {
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .answer-button {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ffc107;
            border: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .answer-button:hover {
            background-color: #ffb300;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Quiz: Teste dein Wissen</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="question">
            <p>Frage 1: Was ist ein tägliches hinduistisches Ritual?</p>
            <button class="answer-button" onclick="alert('Richtig!')">Puja</button>
            <button class="answer-button" onclick="alert('Falsch! Versuche es nochmal.')">Holi</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 Hinduismus Informationen</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
